Package: detectRUNS
Type: Package
Title: Detect Runs of Homozygosity and Runs of Heterozygosity in
    Diploid Genomes
Version: 0.9.6.9000
Date: 2020-12-20
Authors@R: c(
    person("Filippo","Biscarini", email="filippo.biscarini@gmail.com", role=c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Paolo","Cozzi", email="paolo.cozzi@ptp.it", role="aut"),
    person("Giustino","Gaspa", email="gigaspa@uniss.it", role="aut"),
    person("Gabriele","Marras", email="gmarras@uoguelph.ca", role="aut")
  )
Description: Detection of runs of homozygosity and of heterozygosity
    in diploid genomes using two methods: sliding windows (Purcell et al (2007)
    <doi:10.1086/519795>) and consecutive runs (Marras et al (2015)
    <doi:10.1111/age.12259>).
